OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAfghanistan: Biden advised 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto keep 2,500 troops -     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fgenerals                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Two top US generals have said they     
OL,6, recommended keeping a force of 2,500   
OL,7, troops in Afghanistan, ahead of the    
OL,8, full US withdrawal in August.          
OL,10,FTestimony by Gen Mark Milley and Gen   
OL,11,FFrank McKenzie to Congress seemed to   
OL,12,Fcontradict President Joe Biden, who    
OL,13,Fsaid he did not recall any such advice.
OL,15,FThe Taliban took power in August, after
OL,16,Frapidly advancing through the country. 
OL,18,FGen Milley said the US had been taken  
OL,19,Fby surprise by the speed of the Afghan 
OL,20,Fgovernment's collapse.                 
